  <!--Augmented Lanius Spawning Stuff-->


  <textList name="TEXT_ABC_AUGMENTEDLANIUS">
    <text>Oh great, they come in green now. Not a real surprise, considering what your codex told you. It doesn’t matter if it’s just a Lanius, it's still bathed in ancient tech, and you have great disdain for those who use said tech!... Except yourself, you deserve it. You prepare to take said technology, by force.</text>
    <text>It’s the trash eater squad again! This time highly unstable consumers of aether tech - aether tech that should belong to you! You should show them what’s what and take it for yourself... Though you hope they don’t blow up their own ship with that nasty habit of eating their hull.</text>
    <text>As you exit your jump you find the familiar neon green tech of an augmented vessel. For a society that has so much power contained in every single nook and cranny, it’s quite the shame they’ve decided to eat most of it. You better go ahead and kill them before they can munch on whatever is left.</text>
    <text>Your ship whirs its engines down, before immediately kicking them back to life as you find the promised Augmented vessel. You’re not sure what’s more dangerous, their weapons or their crew, but nothing will get in the way of your hunt.</text>
