      Subtype Details: Unique
      Stats: x2.5 repair speed, takes 70% damage from fire and 40% damage from suffocation, x0.6 combat damage
      Ability (30s cooldown, 15s duration): Shields temporarily. Damage from all sources reduced by 80%, resist Mind Control attempts, and reduce suffocation damage taken by 50% for allies.
